\begin_layout Definition
设
\begin_inset Formula $x\left(t\right):[a,b]\to X$
\end_inset

是一个抽象函数, 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{0}\in\left[a,b\right]$
\end_inset

, 若存在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in X$
\end_inset

, 使得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\norm{\frac{x\left(t_{0}+\Delta t\right)-x\left(t\right)}{\Delta t}-x_{0}}=0,
\]

\end_inset

则
\series bold
称
\begin_inset Formula $x\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $t=t_{0}$
\end_inset

点可微
\series default
, 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset


\series bold
称为是
\begin_inset Formula $x\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $t=t_{0}$
\end_inset

点处的导数
\series default
, 记为
\begin_inset Formula $x'\left(t_{0}\right)$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\frac{x\left(t_{0}+\Delta t\right)-x\left(t_{0}\right)}{\Delta t}=x'\left(t_{0}\right),
\]

\end_inset

上面的极限是范数意义下的极限.
 
\end_layout

